name: Waks_Burr
content:
Waks Burr was an Ishi Tib who visited the Outlander Club in the Uscru Entertainment District of the planet Coruscant in the year 22 BBY. Burr wore simple, black overalls while attending the club, and entered the building alongside a female human directly behind the Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi and his padawan Anakin Skywalker, who were there pursuing the bounty hunter Zam Wesell. The Ishi Tib had green skin and brown eyes.
Wakks Burr first appeared in the film Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones, which was released on May 16, 2002. The character was first named by the Legends reference magazine The Official Star Wars Fact File 96, released by De Agostini on October 29, 2003. The name was first used in canon in the reference book Star Wars: The Visual Encyclopedia, released on April 4, 2017.
